{"tid":2258621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何謂五中全會","createTime":"2020-10-26T07:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T07:36:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee9aa4bdfd0b89eec91bea777e428b9bccb311b","tid":2258621,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/PZA5LO4KWJBOFCF2VOPVKJH3QU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FPZA5LO4KWJBOFCF2VOPVKJH3QU%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=6c573b66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FPZA5LO4KWJBOFCF2VOPVKJH3QU%2F&h=2fb54345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/PZA5LO4KWJBOFCF2VOPVKJH3QU/</a><br />\n<br />\n何謂五中全會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jVxecCIbXH1J9vgvs-XjeiCz_-Q=/1822x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/334K35QDPJGHVKGHTREFLWEIXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjVxecCIbXH1J9vgvs-XjeiCz_-Q%3D%2F1822x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F334K35QDPJGHVKGHTREFLWEIXY.jpg&h=9e98ba30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平（左）、李克強（右）<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五中全會今揭幕定2035目標  習硬推雙循環不歸路<br />\n<br />\n中共五年一度舉行全國代表大會，選出新一屆中央委員會，每屆中央委員會在五年任期通常開七次全體會議，每年至少一次。今次舉行的五中全會，全名是「中共第十九屆中央委員會第五次全體會議」，意即是第五次的全體會議，會議一般而言都在京西賓館舉行。今年第十九屆中央委員會委員人數有204人，所有委員都必須出席。今次會議將審議「十四五規劃」，意思是自1953年開始制定第一個「五年計劃」以來，今次是十四個「五年計劃」。"}]}